[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 6.24,
    "text": "Pardon me, would your name be Swampy, ex-drummer for the band Love Handle?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.24,
    "endTime": 8.32,
    "text": "That, my friend, was a past life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.32,
    "endTime": 9.84,
    "text": "The name's Sherman."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.84,
    "endTime": 10.84,
    "text": "Why askin'?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.84,
    "endTime": 13.12,
    "text": "Because they're reforming for one night only."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.12,
    "endTime": 14.92,
    "text": "It's a celebration of our parents' anniversary."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.92,
    "endTime": 20.0,
    "text": "Well, that sounds charming, boys, but I haven't played drums since the accident."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 21.799,
    "text": "Fell asleep in a metronome factory."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.799,
    "endTime": 24.4,
    "text": "When I woke, I'd completely lost my sense of rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.4,
    "endTime": 28.878999999999998,
    "text": "I've been hangin' out here ever since."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.879,
    "endTime": 33.959,
    "text": "So you're sayin' that you don't have rhythm, but listen what you're doin' right there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.959,
    "endTime": 36.56,
    "text": "With that stamp and a book, you got a real nice hook."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.56,
    "endTime": 38.84,
    "text": "Sounds to me like you got rhythm to spare."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.84,
    "endTime": 41.24,
    "text": "I have no idea what you're talkin' about."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.24,
    "endTime": 44.04,
    "text": "I've got as much rhythm as that chair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.04,
    "endTime": 47.958999999999996,
    "text": "What happened to me was a tragedy, but I don't have to be a millionaire."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.959,
    "endTime": 51.24,
    "text": "Look, I got a sweet deal goin' on here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.24,
    "endTime": 53.959,
    "text": "I got all the books that I can read."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.959,
    "endTime": 56.279,
    "text": "All these sweet old ladies in this carpet from the 80s."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.279,
    "endTime": 59.279,
    "text": "One from Wonka to Librarian Neat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.279,
    "endTime": 60.279,
    "text": "Shhh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.279,
    "endTime": 63.279,
    "text": "Besides, I ain't got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.279,
    "endTime": 65.279,
    "text": "No, I ain't got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.279,
    "endTime": 68.279,
    "text": "Said I ain't got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.279,
    "endTime": 71.279,
    "text": "I ain't got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.279,
    "endTime": 72.279,
    "text": "You're kiddin' me, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.279,
    "endTime": 73.279,
    "text": "You're, you're kiddin' me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.279,
    "endTime": 76.279,
    "text": "Don't you see what you were doin' right then?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.279,
    "endTime": 79.279,
    "text": "That's a wicked groove you were startin' to move."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.279,
    "endTime": 81.279,
    "text": "Mister, you got rhythm times ten."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.279,
    "endTime": 83.279,
    "text": "I think perhaps that you're not listenin'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.279,
    "endTime": 86.279,
    "text": "I find it tedious to repeat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.279,
    "endTime": 87.279,
    "text": "It's no big crime."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.279,
    "endTime": 88.279,
    "text": "I just can't keep time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.279,
    "endTime": 91.279,
    "text": "I'm tellin' you, I lost the beat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.279,
    "endTime": 96.279,
    "text": "I don't need my face on T-shirts or hit a power chord guitar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.279,
    "endTime": 97.279,
    "text": "Never scream out my name."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.279,
    "endTime": 101.279,
    "text": "I guess it's a shame, but I don't need to be a rock star."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.279,
    "endTime": 104.279,
    "text": "Besides, I ain't got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.279,
    "endTime": 106.279,
    "text": "No, I ain't got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.279,
    "endTime": 109.279,
    "text": "Said I ain't got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.279,
    "endTime": 112.279,
    "text": "I ain't got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.279,
    "endTime": 113.279,
    "text": "I ain't got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.279,
    "endTime": 114.279,
    "text": "Sounds like rhythm to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.279,
    "endTime": 116.279,
    "text": "No, I ain't got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.279,
    "endTime": 117.279,
    "text": "Seems like they all agree."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.279,
    "endTime": 118.279,
    "text": "I ain't got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.279,
    "endTime": 122.279,
    "text": "But you're layin' down some fuckin' syncopation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.279,
    "endTime": 123.279,
    "text": "I ain't got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.279,
    "endTime": 124.279,
    "text": "But you got that beat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.279,
    "endTime": 125.279,
    "text": "No, I ain't got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.279,
    "endTime": 127.279,
    "text": "Look at them, they're stoppin' their beat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.279,
    "endTime": 128.279,
    "text": "I ain't got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.279,
    "endTime": 132.279,
    "text": "It's time for you to rock a brand new generation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.279,
    "endTime": 134.279,
    "text": "Brand new generation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.279,
    "endTime": 139.279,
    "text": "Gonna rock a brand new generation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.279,
    "endTime": 144.279,
    "text": "Because I ain't got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.279,
    "endTime": 146.279,
    "text": "Would you just go join the band?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.279,
    "endTime": 151.279,
    "text": "Hey, hey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.279,
    "endTime": 152.279,
    "text": "Hey, look at this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.279,
    "endTime": 154.279,
    "text": "Hey, look at this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.279,
    "endTime": 155.279,
    "text": "Check it out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.279,
    "endTime": 158.279,
    "text": "Look at this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.279,
    "endTime": 160.279,
    "text": "Hey, I got rhythm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.279,
    "endTime": 163.279,
    "text": "There's 104 days of summer vacation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.279,
    "endTime": 165.279,
    "text": "And school comes along just to end it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.279,
    "endTime": 170.279,
    "text": " So the annual problem for our generation is finding a girl."
  }
